SUMMARY:Caroline County GOP Lincoln Reagan Dinner
DESCRIPTION:Thursday\, April 23\, 6PM at the American Legion in Denton. We have some amazing silent auction items\, and are so excited for our Keynote Speaker\, Andrew Langer.  Andrew will speak about the importance of living your faith in public service.  And we’ll have members of our state GOP delegation there to give a wrap-up of the just-finished Maryland state legislative session. Plus strategy for the upcoming gubernatorial election and what we need to do to FIGHT for EVERY SEAT! And don’t forget – live auction for Joanne Smith’s famous coconut and carrot cakes.  \n\n\n\nCaroline GOP Lincoln Reagan Dinner 2026 \n\n\n\nThursday\, April 23\, 6PM \n\n\n\nAmerican Legion Post 29 \n\n\n\n9238 Legion Rd\, Denton\, MD \n\n\n\nTickets and Sponsorships: www.CarolineGOP.org
URL:https://mdgop.org/event/caroline-county-gop-lincoln-reagan-dinner/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/webp:https://mdgop.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/30/2026/04/T73DKMTFXFNYVUIIYTAPX3XM.jpeg.webp
ORGANIZER;CN="Caroline County GOP":MAILTO:info@carolinegop.org
END:VEVENT
