SUMMARY:MDGOP Spring 2026 Convention
DESCRIPTION:The date is set and registration is now open! We are officially gathering at Rocky Gap Resort in Allegany County on May 8th and 9th for our Spring 2026 Convention. \n\n\n\nJoin us as we organize\, train volunteers\, meet candidates\, and rally for victory in the 2026 General Election! \n\n\n\nRegister today: https://secure.anedot.com/maryland-republican-party/sc2026 \n\n\n\n\nRegister Here!
URL:https://mdgop.org/event/mdgop-spring-2026-convention/
